00:47:50,413 --> 00:47:52,624
Come inside with you?

524
00:47:55,251 --> 00:47:58,880
It's a lot nicer in there
than it is out here.

525
00:48:06,262 --> 00:48:07,847
You live in there?

526
00:48:10,850 --> 00:48:12,310
By yourself?

527
00:48:12,602 --> 00:48:15,271
No. I have a roommate,
but she's not home.

528
00:48:16,856 --> 00:48:18,233
Hey, it's okay.

529
00:48:19,025 --> 00:48:21,069
Listen, no one will bother us.

530
00:48:22,111 --> 00:48:23,613
It's okay. Come on.

531
00:48:24,364 --> 00:48:25,448
Come on.

532
00:48:51,766 --> 00:48:52,976
This is it.

533
00:48:57,147 --> 00:48:58,648
