538
00:49:31,347 --> 00:49:32,724
It's okay.

539
00:49:48,531 --> 00:49:52,952
Do you suppose we should
talk about money?

540
00:49:53,703 --> 00:49:55,205
Yeah, I guess so.

541
00:49:56,873 --> 00:49:58,958
