544
00:50:15,892 --> 00:50:17,602
What do I recommend?

545
00:50:32,242 --> 00:50:35,119
I'd rather not put it into words.

546
00:50:37,914 --> 00:50:40,083
How about you just leave it up to me?

547
00:50:40,583 --> 00:50:42,377
I'm in your hands.

548
00:50:45,255 --> 00:50:47,841
And how does 1 50 sound?

549
00:50:48,883 --> 00:50:51,344
Sounds wonderful.

550
00:50:55,348 --> 00:50:59,310
Don't worry. I don't
keep track of the time.

551
00:51:07,152 --> 00:51:08,069
Thank you.

552
00:51:08,278 --> 00:51:09,279
Prego, Prego.

553
00:51:09,529 --> 00:51:11,781
-Grazie.
-You're welcome.

554
00:51:12,740 --> 00:51:15,243
If I was Italian, he'd have
answered me in Italian.

555
00:51:59,537 --> 00:52:00,872
Shall we?

556
00:52:19,265 --> 00:52:20,600
Excuse me.

557
00:52:34,906 --> 00:52:36,699
Is everything all right?

558
00:52:40,537 --> 00:52:43,873
I was just wondering if you
were going to be much longer?

559
00:52:45,500 --> 00:52:50,380
Listen, it's a little difficult
to talk right now.

560
00:52:51,214 --> 00:52:53,091
It could be awhile.

561
00:52:54,551 --> 00:52:56,719
Any idea how long?

562
00:52:57,554 --> 00:53:00,014
No, I don't really know.

563
00:53:00,390 --> 00:53:03,142
We're still waiting
