564
00:53:05,228 --> 00:53:09,440
Well, I'm gonna go to bed now.

565
00:53:27,750 --> 00:53:31,504
Was that Mrs. Dr. Bill?

566
00:53:51,774 --> 00:53:53,276
Do you have to go?

567
00:53:54,569 --> 00:53:56,696
Do I have to go?

568
00:54:01,367 --> 00:54:03,036
I think I do.

569
00:54:05,830 --> 00:54:07,248
Are you sure?

570
00:54:13,421 --> 00:54:15,632
Yes, I'm afraid so.

571
00:54:18,885 --> 00:54:21,804
But listen, I want to pay you anyway.

572
00:54:22,305 --> 00:54:26,684
How much did you say it was?
