573
00:54:30,563 --> 00:54:34,150
But you know what? You don't
have to bother about that.

574
00:54:34,359 --> 00:54:35,819
No, it's all right.

575
00:54:36,736 --> 00:54:39,864
-No, really. You don't have to.
-No, I want to.

576
00:54:42,450 --> 00:54:43,409
Really?

577
00:54:45,995 --> 00:54:47,956
Well, thank you very much.

578
00:55:32,709 --> 00:55:33,877
Thank you.

579
00:55:48,391 --> 00:55:51,686
Would you like a table,
