599
00:57:25,530 --> 00:57:26,948
You're married?

600
00:57:27,574 --> 00:57:28,950
Nine years.

601
00:57:29,367 --> 00:57:32,328
-Any kids?
-Yes, we have a 7-year-old daughter.

602
00:57:32,537 --> 00:57:33,580
How about you?

603
00:57:33,788 --> 00:57:36,416
I've got a wife
and four boys in Seattle.

604
00:57:36,624 --> 00:57:38,001
