605
00:57:38,459 --> 00:57:41,129
Well, you gotta go where the work is.

606
00:57:41,963 --> 00:57:42,964
Thank you.

607
00:57:49,053 --> 00:57:51,472
-is this your band?
-No, it's a pick-up band.

608
00:57:51,681 --> 00:57:55,727
-Who do you normally play with?
-Anybody, anywhere.

609
00:57:55,977 --> 00:57:58,438
I got another gig later tonight.

610
00:57:58,646 --> 00:58:00,565
You're playing somewhere else tonight?

611
00:58:00,773 --> 00:58:02,484
They only get started around 2.

612
00:58:03,276 --> 00:58:04,486
in the Village?

613
00:58:06,696 --> 00:58:10,116
Believe it or not, I don't actually
know the address yet.

614
00:58:10,533 --> 00:58:11,576
You don't?

615
00:58:12,243 --> 00:58:16,998
No. it may sound ridiculous, but it's
in a different place every time...

616
00:58:17,207 --> 00:58:20,001
...and I only get it
an hour or so before.

617
00:58:20,210 --> 00:58:22,879
-A different place every time?
-So far.

618
00:58:24,005 --> 00:58:25,215
What's the big mystery?

619
00:58:26,007 --> 00:58:29,260
Hey, man, I just play the piano.

620
00:58:32,972 --> 00:58:36,226
Nick, I'm sorry.
is there something I'm missing here?

621
00:58:39,270 --> 00:58:42,106
I play blindfolded.

622
00:58:43,233 --> 00:58:44,400
What?

623
00:58:46,236 --> 00:58:48,822
I play blindfolded.

624
00:58:52,867 --> 00:58:54,410
You're putting me on.

625
00:58:54,619 --> 00:58:57,080
No, it's the truth.

626
00:58:58,081 --> 00:59:02,710
And the last time,
the blindfold wasn't on so well.

627
00:59:05,088 --> 00:59:06,798
Oh, man.

628
00:59:07,966 --> 00:59:12,303
Bill, I have seen one or two things
in my life...

629
00:59:12,679 --> 00:59:14,347
...but never...

630
00:59:14,722 --> 00:59:17,141
...never anything like this...

631
00:59:17,892 --> 00:59:20,937
...and never such women.

632
00:59:31,197 --> 00:59:32,448
Excuse me.

633
00:59:36,327 --> 00:59:39,372
Yes, sir.
Yes, sir, this is Nick.

634
00:59:45,211 --> 00:59:47,046
I know where that is.

635
00:59:54,637 --> 00:59:55,597
Right.

636
00:59:59,225 --> 01:00:01,144
Well, I'm on my way right now.

637
01:00:01,895 --> 01:00:04,439
Okay, sir. Thank you.

638
01:00:06,858 --> 01:00:08,151
What is this?

639
01:00:09,736 --> 01:00:12,363
It's the name of a Beethoven opera,
isn't it?

640
01:00:17,160 --> 01:00:18,828
it's the password.

641
01:00:19,579 --> 01:00:21,080
