Mostly here.

715
01:06:02,672 --> 01:06:04,674
Look at this. Here.

716
01:06:06,009 --> 01:06:07,135
You see?

717
01:06:07,844 --> 01:06:09,012
And?

718
01:06:09,888 --> 01:06:12,140
I'm afraid this really isn't my field.

719
01:06:12,348 --> 01:06:14,350
What? You can't help me?

720
01:06:14,559 --> 01:06:18,146
No. You should see a trichologist.
it's a hair specialist.

721
01:06:18,354 --> 01:06:21,983
Mr. Milich, I've obviously
left things a bit late tonight.

722
01:06:22,192 --> 01:06:23,902
So if you don't mind--

723
01:06:24,110 --> 01:06:26,196
I'm in hurry too, to get back to bed.

724
01:06:26,404 --> 01:06:27,697
I understand.

725
01:06:28,698 --> 01:06:30,283
So black cloak?

726
01:06:35,205 --> 01:06:36,623
Did you hear something?

727
01:06:39,918 --> 01:06:41,503
What is this?

728
01:06:51,221 --> 01:06:53,014
What is it?

729
01:06:58,102 --> 01:07:00,063
What is this?

730
01:07:13,785 --> 01:07:16,454
What on earth is going on here?!

731
01:07:16,663 --> 01:07:18,790
Milich, I can explain everything.

732
01:07:18,998 --> 01:07:21,292
You! What are you doing here?

733
01:07:21,501 --> 01:07:23,294
I promise I'll kill you!

734
01:07:23,545 --> 01:07:27,423
And you!
Have you no sense of decency?

735
01:07:27,632 --> 01:07:31,427
Gentlemen, have you
no sense of decency?!

736
01:07:31,636 --> 01:07:35,265
Milich, are you crazy? We were
invited here by the young lady.

737
01:07:35,473 --> 01:07:39,853
Young lady? This is my daughter!
Couldn't you see she's a child?

738
01:07:40,103 --> 01:07:42,856
-You will have to explain to police!
-To the police?!

739
01:07:43,064 --> 01:07:45,900
You little whore!
I kill you for this.

740
01:07:46,109 --> 01:07:49,696
I promise, I'll kill you!
I'll kill you!

741
01:07:49,904 --> 01:07:52,073
Hold on to that girl for me, please!

742
01:07:52,282 --> 01:07:56,202
Milich, this is preposterous.
The young lady invited us here.

743
01:07:56,452 --> 01:07:58,538
Couldn't you see she is deranged?!

744
01:07:58,705 --> 01:08:00,331
Doctor, I'm sorry to keep you waiting.

745
01:08:00,582 --> 01:08:03,376
Gentlemen, this is now a police matter.

746
01:08:03,626 --> 01:08:06,254
You will please stay here
until I return.

747
01:08:06,421 --> 01:08:08,047
Let us out of here!

748
01:08:08,214 --> 01:08:10,175
That's out of the question.

749
01:08:10,466 --> 01:08:13,970
Doctor, sorry.
What color did you say?

750
01:08:14,220 --> 01:08:15,763
-Black?
-Black.

751
01:08:16,473 --> 01:08:20,101
Gentlemen, please have the goodness
to be quiet for the moment!

752
01:08:20,268 --> 01:08:22,520
Couldn't you see
I try to serve my customer?

753
01:08:22,812 --> 01:08:23,646
Sorry.

754
01:08:24,272 --> 01:08:27,817
And you, little whore, go to bed
at once, you depraved creature.

755
01:08:28,067 --> 01:08:30,403
I'll deal with you
after I serve this gentleman.

756
01:08:31,196 --> 01:08:33,907
You should have a cloak
lined with ermine.

757
01:10:20,805 --> 01:10:22,974
Okay, that's $74.50.

758
01:10:23,725 --> 01:10:27,562
Seventy-four fifty. All right.

759
01:10:28,730 --> 01:10:30,273
There's 80.

760
01:10:30,773 --> 01:10:33,526
I promised you 50 bucks
over the meter, right?

761
01:10:35,904 --> 01:10:39,282
I'll make that a hundred,
if you wait for me.

762
01:10:39,532 --> 01:10:41,075
Just let the meter run.

763
01:10:41,326 --> 01:10:44,704
I'll give you the other half
plus the meter when I get back.

764
01:10:44,829 --> 01:10:47,499
-Okay?
-How long you gonna be?

765
01:10:47,749 --> 01:10:51,127
I don't know, maybe an hour or more.
But maybe only 1 0 minutes.

766
01:10:52,337 --> 01:10:54,255
I'll leave my stuff here in the back.

767
01:11:12,190 --> 01:11:13,525
Good evening, sir.

768
01:11:14,484 --> 01:11:15,777
Good evening.

769
01:11:16,444 --> 01:11:17,821
Can we be of any help?

770
01:11:19,489 --> 01:11:21,407
I suppose you'd like the password.

771
01:11:21,658 --> 01:11:23,201
If you'd like, sir.

772
01:11:23,660 --> 01:11:24,452
Fidelio.

773
01:11:24,702 --> 01:11:27,747
Thank you, sir.
We'll run you up to the house.

774
01:12:07,871 --> 01:12:09,539
Good evening, sir.

775
01:12:09,789 --> 01:12:11,124
Good evening.

776
01:12:11,416 --> 01:12:13,001
Password, sir?

777
01:12:13,793 --> 01:12:14,794
Fidelio.

778
01:12:15,420 --> 01:12:16,838
